04e944f52868df6de98b79229c0c69f63311b304","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F9Jzfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F9Jzfc.jpg&h=b2709c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242e64c5360f02e56147ae3a2284b1ae03a087c1","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:06:36.000Z","msg":"內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進透露，中國正計劃將《香港人權與民主法案》的起草人，列入禁止入境名單，禁止他們進入中國大陸、香港及澳門。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽表示，一般不會具體回應傳媒、學者、專家、智庫的報道，但重申中方的原則立場，指簽證問題是一國的主權，中國政府當然有權決定容許誰人入境，不容許誰人入境，那些不受歡迎的人，自然不會被容許入境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PBvHQwN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBvHQwN.gif&h=9f4995e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ebd6effcc45de67d55c18142415b6c0a7fa3bc7","tid":1761404,"uid":28296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">can confirm 洗頭 now??<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c1b1cf591869e83fb23f29e28ce7b7700d7e20d7","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xuvkDvt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxuvkDvt.jpg&h=af2361bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一日反狗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12852649ffd57fe3cea62309278e4b39c22f4242","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"耿爽模擬器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1762842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1762842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5D5kHqe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5D5kHqe.jpg&h=0a3e0b49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e550675626c42d55883c6066b0924fad311d80cc","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"记者：4CD7PCBC警🐶，中方对此有何回应？<br />\n<br />\n耿爽：中方就这一问题已多次表明立场：中国坚持走和平发展道路，积极为维护世界和平稳定贡献智慧力量。我们希望4C认真对待中方的严正交涉和严正立场，立即停止不负责任的言行，停止干涉中国内政。我们奉劝某些政客别再浪费4C纳税人的钱，无事生非。中国政府反对任何外部势力干预中国事务的决心坚定不移，维护国家主权、安全、发展利益的决心坚定不移。<br />\n<br />\n中国一向秉持和平共处五项原则处理国与国关系，历来坚定奉行不干涉内政原则，主张各国根据自身国情选择发展道路。中国政府和中国人民坚决反对4CD7PCBC警🐶的行为，中方已就此向4C提出严正交涉和强烈抗议。4C有关人士的陈词滥调充满了政治偏见与谎言。我们奉劝某些政客别再浪费4C纳税人的钱，无事生非。<br />\n<br />\n我要强调，中国内政不容任何外部反华势力指手画脚。中方已就此向4C提出严正交涉，表达强烈抗议。中国一向秉持和平共处五项原则处理国与国关系，历来坚定奉行不干涉内政原则，主张各国根据自身国情选择发展道路。我们奉劝某些政客别再浪费4C纳税人的钱，无事生非。我要告诉4C一些政客，人贵有自知之明，请他还是趁早反省一下4C自身的问题，放弃偏见和执念，停止喋喋不休的反华聒噪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f1a10c97b9242c57cc61e36378b3ca1282d2d5","tid":1761404,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"抽得返暗龍王<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3839b7ce5546848a00e4c728c289213b7bf85d","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/hYmPAfj.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd896cc939bc857db0c9b5709e0bfec24f4c3a3","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54f1a10c97b9242c57cc61e36378b3ca1282d2d5","tid":1761404,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"抽得返暗龍王<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"WUFFL..."},{"pid":"fe0bfdc4280a32f0f495ed6f7e05bc0add58043c","tid":1761404,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T18:47:19.000Z","msg":"D7PCBC警🐶"},{"pid":"f236a8d82c88d63